flowRoot.flowPara: 🌟🌟🌟 Tackle - Move again after attacking, if any movement remains.
🌟🌟🌟 Hurl - Move again after throwing, if any movement remains.
🌟 Sprint - Roll against Agility, if successful, move 2 additional hexes. Sprinting can exceed your normal range.
